## 5 · حالات الـ State في الشاشة

```dart
// BlocConsumer — state له side effects (toast على error)
BlocConsumer<{Name}Cubit, {Name}State>(
  listener: (context, state) {
    state.maybeWhen(
      error: (msg) => context.feedback.error(msg),
      success: () => context.router.pop(true),
      orElse: () {},
    );
  },
  builder: (context, state) => state.when(
    initial: () => const SizedBox.shrink(),
    loading: () => const LoadingWidget(),
    loaded: (data) => {Name}Body(data: data),
    error: (_) => const SizedBox.shrink(),
  ),
)

// BlocBuilder — state بدون side effects
BlocBuilder<{Name}Cubit, {Name}State>(
  builder: (context, state) => state.when(
    initial: () => const SizedBox.shrink(),
    loading: () => const LoadingWidget(),
    loaded: (data) => {Name}Body(data: data),
    error: (msg) => ErrorStateWidget(
      messageKey: msg,
      onRetry: () => context.read<{Name}Cubit>().load(),
    ),
  ),
)
```

